@startuml
title D3: Create a Medical Report

actor "Doctor" as Doctor
participant "Frontend (UI)\n(CreateEMR.tsx)" as UI
participant "MedicalReportController\n(app/routers/reports.py)" as API
participant "CRUD Layer\n(crud.py)" as CRUD
database "PostgreSQL\nDatabase" as DB

Doctor -> UI: Fill EMR form (Notes, Diagnosis, Rx)\nand click "Save"
activate UI

UI -> API: POST /medical_reports/\n(EMR data payload)
activate API

note right of API
  Validates data using
  Pydantic schemas
end note

API -> CRUD: create_medical_report(validatedData)
activate CRUD

CRUD -> DB: INSERT into medical_reports table
activate DB

DB --> CRUD: Return created record ID
deactivate DB

CRUD --> API: Return success object
deactivate CRUD

API --> UI: Return 200 OK & Success Message
deactivate API

UI --> Doctor: Display "Medical Record Saved"
deactivate UI

@enduml